# Group Categories/Categories
`parent` is the category that the current category is a sub-category of.


## Subcategories Collection [/categories/:id/categories?include=includes&limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the parent Category to perform action with.
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `parent` or `all`

